cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.SE, cs.AR 

This paper deals with a type system for resource analysis and control in functional programming languages, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also introduces a categorical semantics, which is related to logic in computer science (cs.LO). The type system is based on a semiring, which is a mathematical structure used in data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses an application to hardware compilation, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper deals with automatic timing analysis, which is related to computer architecture (cs.AR).
